📁 SECURE FLAP & CORD CLOSURE - The folder’s full-size flexible flap and cord closure provide added security. To access stored items, simply fold back the flap. When finished, return the flap up and over the top of the folder and secure it in place using the cord closure.

📁 EXPANDABLE & LARGE CAPACITY - Expandable 12 colors individual pockets for reliable partitioning for A4 size/letter size paper. Each pocket offers a generous amount of space, expanding to 10 inches. It’s expandable bottom adds additional capacity.

📁 UNIQUE DESIGN - Expanding file organizer is advanced than other traditional briefcase.Our rainbow file organizer is 12 individual pockets with cover, and enough long cord flexible elastic closer for safer storage, besides humanized pen holder design, never worry about papers or pens lost, 2 transparent name card slots displayed on the front page.

📁 MULTI-USE & TIME SAVING - The pockets are tabbed to allow for adding handwritten labels, ensuring each section can be instantly identified for quick access. Keeping your holiday documents, vouchers, cards and coupons etc tidy and organised, perfect document organizer for home, office, school use and travel, simple and fashion.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Budget friendly organization
reviews.reviewText: As someone constantly seeking practical yet budget-friendly organization solutions, I stumbled upon this gem of an Accordion File Storage Folder that has truly exceeded my expectations.Let’s start with the build quality. Despite its incredibly affordable price point, this folder doesn’t compromise on durability. The sturdy material ensures that it stands the test of time, accommodating various documents without tearing or losing its shape. The reinforced edges and well-designed accordion-style expandable pockets make it a reliable option for organizing papers, receipts, coupons, and more.The versatility of this folder is remarkable. With multiple compartments and labels, I found it effortless to sort and categorize my documents, keeping everything neat and easily accessible. The expandable nature allows for ample storage capacity while maintaining a compact and portable design, perfect for home, office, or on-the-go use.Moreover, the practicality of this folder shines through its user-friendly design. The secure closure ensures that the contents stay in place, preventing any accidental spills or misplacement of documents. The tabs and labels make identification and retrieval of specific documents a breeze, saving time and eliminating the frustration of rummaging through piles of papers.The affordability of this folder is a definite highlight. Despite being priced competitively, it doesn’t compromise on functionality or quality. It’s a fantastic option for anyone on a budget who doesn’t want to sacrifice organization and efficiency.Additionally, I was pleasantly surprised by the vibrant color options available, adding a touch of personality to an otherwise mundane office accessory. The variety of colors makes it easy to color-code different categories of documents, enhancing the organizational process.In conclusion, this Accordion File Storage Folder combines affordability, durability, functionality, and versatility seamlessly. Its ability to keep documents organized, secure, and easily accessible makes it a go-to choice for anyone seeking a cost-effective yet reliable solution for managing their paperwork.
